%20to%20consider%20all%20the%20other%20costs%20I%20might%20face.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20always%20kept%20our%20finances%20and%20investments%20separate.%20But%20recently%2C%20we%20have%20started%20to%20commingle%20some%20of%20our%20money%20and%20work%20together%20on%20joint%20goals.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20opened%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-joint-bank-accounts%5C%22%3Ejoint%20bank%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-open-a-joint-credit-card%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fund%20our%20family%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20we're%20strategizing%20a%20few%20ways%20we%20can%20invest%20our%20cash%20together%20to%20diversify%20our%20portfolios.%20One%20thing%20we've%20been%20discussing%20is%20the%20option%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-invest-in-gold%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20gold%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20our%20friends%20recently%20bought%20gold%20bars%20to%20diversify%20their%20investment%20portfolios.%20Since%20we%20were%20interested%20in%20this%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20speak%20with%20certified%20financial%20planner%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sparkwealthadvisors.com%2Fabout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJake%20Skelhorn%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20It%20might%20not%20be%20the%20best%20option%20for%20inflation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Skelhorn%20why%20people%20buy%20gold%20bars%2C%20he%20said%20the%20most%20common%20reason%20is%20that%20they%20want%20to%20use%20them%20to%20hedge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-inflation%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20market%20gets%20rocky%2C%20people%20try%20to%20seek%20something%20that%20seems%20safer%20or%20keeps%20them%20away%20from%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20investing%20in%20gold%20isn't%20always%20the%20best%20way%20to%20fight%20off%20inflation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20Skelhorn%20said%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20can%20fluctuate%20drastically.%20Even%20though%20the%20demand%20for%20gold%20will%20increase%20when%20there's%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20the%20actual%20prices%20of%20gold%20aren't%20tied%20to%20inflation%20but%20to%20supply%20and%20demand%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20protect%20your%20money%20from%20inflation%2C%20Skelhorn%20recommends%20a%20longer-term%20strategy%20involving%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-a-bond%5C%22%3Ebonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Gold%20is%20taxed%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESkelhorn%20emphasized%20that%20gold%20is%20taxed%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%20than%20normal%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCapital%20gain%20taxes%20for%20gold%20are%2028%25%20when%20it's%20held%20over%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOther%20assets%20like%20stocks%20or%20real%20estate%20could%20be%20taxed%20at%200-20%25%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20total%20income%20for%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20tax-friendly%20investment%20vehicle%2C%20Skelhorn%20mentioned%20it's%20possible%20to%20instead%20invest%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-gold-ira%5C%22%3Egold%20IRA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20capital%20gain%20tax%20when%20you%20buy%20or%20sell%20the%20funds%20inside%20the%20IRA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20There's%20no%20income%20related%20to%20investing%20in%20gold%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20factor%20Skelhorn%20advised%20me%20to%20consider%20is%20that%20I%20can't%20earn%20income%20by%20buying%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComparing%20it%20to%20stocks%20or%20bonds%2C%20which%20could%20yield%20interest%20or%20dividends%2C%20there's%20no%20income%20when%20you%20buy%20gold%20bars%20because%20you're%20just%20holding%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkelhorn%20added%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20make%20money%20off%20gold%20bars%20is%20by%20selling%20them%20for%20more%20than%20you%20bought%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Investing%20in%20gold%20can%20diversify%20your%20portfolio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESkelhorn%20did%20confirm%20that%20investing%20in%20gold%20could%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20diversify%20my%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGold%20isn't%20correlated%20with%20other%20asset%20classes%20like%20the%20stock%20market%20or%20bonds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20the%20stock%20market%20goes%20down%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20will%20go%20down%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20that%20before%20buying%20gold%20bars%2C%20we%20should%20understand%20there%20could%20be%20added%20fees%20depending%20on%20how%20we%20buy%20and%20store%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3EWhether%20you're%20opening%20a%20Gold%20IRA%20or%20buying%20physical%20gold%20to%20diversify%20your%20portfolio%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fgoldco-review%5C%22%3EGoldco%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20you%20seamlessly%20navigate%20the%20process.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.money.com%2Fpr%2Fs3040749cb4d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERequest%20a%20free%20kit%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fgoldco-review%5C%22%3EGoldco%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F