0repercussions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.predictit.org%2Fmarkets%2Fdetail%2F7456%2FWho-will-win-the-2024-US-presidential-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eodds%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20Donald%20Trump%20White%20House%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Ftrump-election-odds-treasury-bond-yields-inflation-deficit-debt-economy-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20high%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20economists%20and%20market%20forecasters%20have%20been%20wrapping%20their%20heads%20around%20what%20the%20new%20regime%20will%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20most%20things%20Trump-related%2C%20there's%20a%20serious%20divide%20between%20outlooks%2C%20and%20his%20fiscal%20platform%20is%20no%20different.%20Experts%20hold%20drastically%20different%20views%2C%20creating%20a%20new%20hot-button%20topic%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20debated%20up%20until%20the%20election%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20proposed%20fiscal%20path%20contains%20multiple%20elements%2C%20the%20first%20being%20tariffs.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20tilt%20trade%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20US%2C%20Trump%20has%20made%20wide-sweeping%20duties%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20international%20platform.%20Virtually%20all%20US%20imports%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-plan-inflation-policy-impact-trade-war-china-rates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaxed%20at%2010%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he's%20said%2C%20though%20this%20rate%20would%20be%20as%20high%20as%2060%25%20for%20key%20competitors%2C%20such%20as%20China.%20It's%20a%20much%20more%20aggressive%20approach%20than%20Biden's%20actions%20so%20far%2C%20which%20have%20included%20a%20100%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20tariffs%20in%20place%20of%20the%20US%20income%20tax.%20The%20plan%20was