cently%20made%20the%20argument%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F07%2F02%2Fopinion%2Ftariffs-trump-china-taxes.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%20op-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20would%20benefit%20only%20the%20wealthiest%20Americans.%20He%20also%20predicted%20that%2080%25%20of%20US%20consumers%20would%20end%20up%20losing%20after-tax%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20numerical%20terms%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20estimated%20that%20the%20policies%20would%20cause%20US%20GDP%20to%20drop%200.5%25%2C%20while%20pushing%20inflation%20up%201.1%20percentage%20point.%20The%20firm%20says%20that's%20enough%20to%20force%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-trade-policy-barrier-income-tax-rate-hikes-krugman-2024-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTrump%2527s%2520wide%252Dreaching%2520tariff%2520plan%2C%2525%252C%2520Nobel%252Dwinning%2520economist%2520says%26amp%3Btext%3DTrump%2527s%2520proposed%2520tariffs%2520would%2520benefit%2C%252Dtax%2520income%252C%2520he%2520said%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E130-basis-point%20increase%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20interest%20rates%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20most%20investors%20want%20borrowing%20costs%20to%20climb%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peterson%20Institute%20offers%20a%20more%20drastic%20outcome%3A%20a%20full-fledged%20global%20trade%20war.%20The%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank%20notes%20that%20the%20last%20time%20blanket%20tariffs%20were%20implemented%20nearly%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-trade-war-risk-china-exports-great-depression-economy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtributed%20to%20the%20Great%20Depression%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20shares%20this%20degree%20of%20skepticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c18cb08-2648-4da1-af4b-98e9f0a497cf%5C%22%3EThe%20camp%20that%20says%20it%20won't%20be%20as%20bad%20as%20fe