s%20Trump%20is%20intentionally%20over-exaggerating%20his%20plan%2C%20and%20what%20he%20would%20actually%20enact%20would%20be%20more%20restrained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHyperbole%20is%20useful%20to%20kick%20the%20hornet's%20nest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd0dgI5AxhzY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22058337c1-4aba-4ec1-9982-ed5e410d4845%5C%22%3EIt%20ultimately%20depends%20on%20Congress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nobel%20prize-winning%20economist%20Joseph%20Stiglitz%20represents%20a%20sort%20of%20middle%20ground%20between%20the%20two%20polarized%20factions.%20Although%20he%20was%20one%20of%2016%20economists%20to%20sign%20an%20open%20letter%20warning%20that%20Trump's%20policies%20could%20drive%20inflation%20higher%2C%20he%20also%20says%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20Yardeni%20%E2%80%94%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-presidency-policies-inflation-economy-americans-joseph-stiglitz-letter-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20depends%20on%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20general%20consensus%2C%20not%20just%20my%20view%2C%20but%20almost%20anybody%20modeling%20what%20is%20going%20on%20would%20say%20the%20Trump%20administration%20would%20be%20more%20inflationary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20more%20depends%20on%20how%20radical%20they%20are.%20And%20that%20depends%20on%20where%20Congress%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20from%20Oxford%20Economics%20shows%20these%20unique%20dynamics%20in%20action.%20Although%20the%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-blown%20Trump%26quot%3B%20administration%20would%20be%20the%20most%20inflationary%20outcome%20during%20the%20next%20presidential%20term%2C%20the%20data%20shows%20that%20a%20Trump%20win%20under%20a%20divided%20government%20would%20be%20less%20inflationary%20than%20a%20