have%20ever%20known.%20And%20that%20intelligence%20carved%20out%20her%20witty%20sense%20of%20humor%2C%20%26quot%3Bquick%20as%20a%20whip%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20stated%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchildhood-best-friend-lost-touch-reconnect-college-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildhood%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20my%20mom%2C%20and%20I%20can't%20remember%20her%20as%20well%20as%20I%20would%20like%20to.%20I%20lost%20her%2010%20days%20before%20my%208th%20birthday%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20quite%20emotionally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-mom-died-aunt-adopted-me-family-grief-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeal%20with%20her%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20I%20turned%2012%20or%2013.%20I%20just%20couldn't%20comprehend%20what%20it%20meant%20when%20someone%20died%2C%20let%20alone%20my%20own%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22287fc376-b2ce-4e20-8c17-4732f5d6d6a7%5C%22%3EI%20only%20have%20eight%20years%20of%20memories%20with%20her%2C%20but%20I%20cherish%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20the%20woman%20who%20would%20iron%20my%20clothes%20religiously%2C%20put%20matching%20bows%20in%20my%20hair%20before%20school%2C%20and%20always%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eput%20notes%20in%20my%20lunchbox.%20I%20remember%20how%20the%20notes%20started.%20I%20saw%20another%20child%20at%20lunch%20who%20would%20get%20notes%2C%20and%20I%20went%20home%2C%20sheepishly%20asking%20if%20my%20mom%20would%20do%20the%20same.%20I%20never%20had%20to%20ask%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20my%20mom's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpreemie-baby-weight-guilt-parents-miracle-pressure-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emiracle%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20struggled%20with%20pregnancies%20and%20had%20fully%20given%20up%20on%20trying%20to%20have%20a%20child.%20That's%20how%20it%20almost%20always%20works%2C%20right%3F%20My%20mom%20gave%20birth%20to%20me%20in