0Abrams%20tanks%20that%20is%20able%20to%20detect%20targets%20out%20to%20a%20distance%20of%20five%20miles.%20Its%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20armor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20plate%20on%20the%20front%20of%20its%20belly%2C%20are%20durable%20enough%20to%20protect%20against%20some%20munitions%20and%20shield%20it%20against%20certain%20mine%20explosions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bradley's%20armor%20can%20also%20be%20bolstered%20with%20explosive%20reactive%20armor%2C%20like%20a%20main%20battle%20tank%2C%20to%20further%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20US%20Army%20infantry%20officer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20%26quot%3Bthe%20capabilities%20that%20it%20brings%20in%20terms%20of%20speed%2C%20its%20ability%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20tanks%2C%20your%20ability%20to%20move%20infantry%20squads%20in%20a%20protected%20manner%20across%20the%20battlefield%20very%20quickly%2C%20and%20its%20fairly%20robust%20armor%20package%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20weapons%20systems%20on%20there%20%E2%80%94%20make%20it%20a%20very%20effective%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20announced%20it%20would%20send%20dozens%20of%20Bradleys%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20early%202023%20amid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-getting-first-western-armored-combat-vehicles-france-germany-us-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epush%20by%20other%20NATO%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20surge%20armored%20vehicles%20to%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20a%20counteroffensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bradley%20isn't%20the%20only%20armor%20the%20US%20sent%20to%20Ukraine.%20Kyiv%20also%20has%2031%20Abrams%20tanks%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20more%20than%20300%20Bradleys%20it%20has%20received%20as%20of%20early%20July%2C%20according%20to%20Pentagon%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMain%20battle%20tanks%2C%20like%20the%20Abrams%2C%20have%20not%20necessarily%20been%20a%20go-to%20armor%20choice%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20