0workers%20are%20already%20busy%20with%20deliveries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20Flex%20driver%20in%20Alabama%20explained%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20in%20delivering%20all%20that%20stuff%20you%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-amazon-prime%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%20sale%20doesn't%20start%20until%20July%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20one%20Amazon%20Flex%20delivery%20worker%20in%20Alabama%2C%20work%20started%20picking%20up%20this%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker%20said%20she%20picked%20up%20six%20%26quot%3Bblocks%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20shifts%20between%20three%20and%20six%20hours%20long.%20That's%20more%20than%20the%20worker%20has%20usually%20been%20able%20to%20claim%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20basically%20booked%20up%20for%20an%20entire%20week%2C%20which%20really%20doesn't%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20they%20are%20making%20sure%20to%20get%20all%20of%20the%20regular%20stuff%20out%20in%20anticipation%26quot%3B%20of%20Prime%20Day%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flex%20worker%2C%20who%20made%20deliveries%20for%20Amazon%20during%20Prime%20Day%20in%202023%2C%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20name%2C%20but%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20identity%20and%20work%20for%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20Amazon%20delivery%20workers%2C%20Prime%20Day%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20times%20of%20the%20year.%20The%202024%20version%20of%20the%20event%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20on%20July%2016%20and%2017%2C%20promises%20to%20be%20no%20different%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fearly-amazon-prime-day-deals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20has%20already%20spent%20weeks%20promoting%20some%20discounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20deals.%20It's%20promising%20new%20deals%20for%20shoppers%20every%20five%20minutes%20during%20the%20event%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Prime%20Day%20will%20also%20occur%20the%20same%20week%20as%20Alabama's%20tax-free%20weekend%2C%20a%20three-day%20period%20when%20shoppers%20can%20stock%20up%20on%20supplies%20for%20the%20new%20school%20year%20without%20paying%20sales%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20employs%20a%20few%20different%20kinds%20of%20delivery%20workers.%20Those%20who%20work%20through%20the%20company's%20Flex%20program%20are%20independent%20contractors%20using%20their%20own%20cars%20and%20are%20paid%20by%20the%20block.%20Making%20certain%20types%20of%20deliveries%2C%20such%20as%20grocery%20orders%20from%20Whole%20Foods%2C%20comes%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20earn%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flex%20worker%20BI%20spoke%20with%20says%20she's%20seen%20more%20new%20faces%20at%20the%20Amazon%20facilities%20she%20frequents%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%2C%20she%20said%2C%20that%20Amazon%20is%20staffing%20up%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20banner%20shopping%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrime%20Day%2C%20and%20then%20right%20around%20October%2C%20those%20are%20the%20two%20biggest%20times%20when%20they%20hire%20people%20because%20that's%20when%20everybody's%20shopping%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20told%20BI%2C%20referencing%20the%20fall%20increase%20in%20hiring%20ahead%20of%20the%20holiday%20shopping%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20challenge%20for%20Flex%20workers%20is%20delivering%20all%20those%20packages%20within%20the%20time%20allotted%20for%20the%20block%2C%20the%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker%20recalled%20delivering%20about%2030%20packages%20per%20three-and-a-half-hour%20block%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Lately%2C%20though%2C%20the%20worker%20has%20noticed%20that%20number%20reaching%20closer%20to%2040%2C%20especially%20during%20evening%20delivery%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20don't%20do%20it%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bthey'll%20just%20say%20you're%20unreliable%2C%20and%20you're%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20shifts%20with%20the%20best%20pay%20also%20requires%20a%20strategy%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20normal%20week%20in%20her%20area%2C%20a%20three-and-a-half%20hour%20block%20of%20delivering%20packages%20pays%20%2463%2C%20the%20driver%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20That%20rate%20can%20go%20above%20%2480%20if%20drivers%20wait%20until%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20before%20a%20shift%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20Prime%20Day%2C%20those%20higher%20offers%20come%20up%20sooner%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20full%20day%20before%20the%20shift%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20are%20also%20competing%20with%20the%20influx%20of%20new%20drivers%20around%20the%20event.%20Speaking%20to%20BI%20on%20the%20Thursday%20before%20Prime%20Day%2C%20the%20Flex%20driver%20said%20she%20still%20hadn't%20seen%20any%20blocks%20for%20next%20week%2C%20but%20she's%20ready%20to%20grab%20whatever%20shifts%20she%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20just%20hits%20bigger%20and%20quicker%26quot%3B%20around%20the%20shopping%20extravaganza%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20driver%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Amazon%20Flex%20program%20gives%20individuals%20the%20opportunity%20to%20set%20their%20own%20schedule%20and%20be%20their%20own%20boss%2C%20while%20earning%20competitive%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20Branden%20Baribeau%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20Flex%20delivery%20partners%20are%20able%20to%20work%20when%20they%20want%20%E2%80%93%20including%20on%20and%20around%20Prime%20Day%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20vast%20majority%20finishing%20their%20delivery%20blocks%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20Baribeau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20something%20like%20a%20delivery%20partner%20repeatedly%20not%20showing%20up%20for%20a%20scheduled%20block%20or%20not%20foll