o%20(left)%20and%20his%20mom%2C%20Ivette%20Cuevas%20(right)%20in%20the%20basket%20of%20a%20hot%20air%20balloon.%3Cp%3EVincent%20Alcampo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIvette%20Cuevas%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20with%20her%20son%2C%20Vincent%20Alcampo%2C%2010%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20relationship%20that%20drew%20Ivette%20there%20ended%2C%20but%20they%20say%20Costa%20Rican%20life%20suits%20them..%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIvette%20remarried%20and%20started%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Vincent%20manages%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20have%20plans%20to%20expand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Ivette%20Cuevas%2C%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20owner%20living%20in%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20and%20her%2016-year-old%20son%2C%20Vincent%20Alcampo.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIvette%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20didn't%20choose%20Costa%20Rica%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20chose%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20California%2010%20years%20ago%20to%20build%20a%20new%20life%20with%20my%20business%20and%20romantic%20partner.%20Together%2C%20we%20purchased%20a%20hotel%20with%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Uvita%2C%20a%20beach%20town%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcosta-rica-pacific-coast-travel-guide-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosta%20Rica's%20Pacific%20coast%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20had%20no%20experience%20running%20a%20restaurant%20and%20initially%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%20the%20hotel's%20day-to-day%20operations%20%E2%80%94%20but%20when%20we%20split%20up%2C%20I%20took%20over%20the%20restaurant%20while%20he%20managed%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wound%20up%20selling%20the%20restaurant%20before%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20let%20go.%20It%20became%20my%20dream%20to%20open%20a%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20breakup%2C%20life%