20and%20let%20me%20take%20on%20a%20full-time%20job%20after%20I%20tested%20out%20of%20my%20senior%20year%20of%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIvette%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20had%20been%20eyeing%20a%20property%20nearby%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bfor%20rent%26quot%3B%20sign%20for%20months.%20From%20the%20moment%20I%20called%20to%20see%20if%20the%20place%20was%20even%20available%2C%20everything%20just%20fell%20into%20place.%20I%20just%20knew%20it%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20so%20Coffee%20Bear%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20created%20a%20menu%20from%20scratch%20based%20on%20breakfast%20recipes%20for%20foods%20I%20missed%20from%20back%20home.%20I%20wanted%20simple%20ingredients%2C%20quick%20service%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcosta-rica-blue-zone-diet-nicoya-peninsula-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthier%20alternative%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fast%20food%2C%20which%20is%20all%20over%20the%20place%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20cater%20to%20locals%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0mostly%20ex-pats%20from%20the%20States%20and%20Canada%20since%20we're%20near%20the%20US%20Embassy%2C%20but%20the%20odd%20tourist%20finds%20us%20off%20the%20beaten%20path%20every%20now%20and%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20wouldn't%20be%20what%20it%20is%20without%20Vincent.%20He's%2016%20but%20an%20old%20soul%20and%20so%20ambitious%20for%20his%20age.%20He's%20taken%20on%20a%20huge%20role%20at%20Coffee%20Bear%2C%20and%20together%2C%20we're%20planning%20to%20open%20a%20second%20location%20near%20the%20beach%20in%20Guanacaste%20that'd%20be%20his%20to%20run.%20We're%20looking%20at%20building%20him%20a%20small%20house%20up%20there%20to%20live%20in%20while%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVincent%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20the%20coffee%20shop%2C%20I%20get%20to%20do%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20everything%3A%20managing%2C%20being%20a%20barista%2C%20working%20the%20cash%20register.%20It's%20different%20ev