re.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocating-costa-rica-best-thing-california-woman-and-her-son-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720868282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6680b01ad1c84a0eaca90e61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocating-costa-rica-best-thing-california-woman-and-her-son-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ivette%20Cuevas%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20and%20opened%20a%20coffee%20shop%20with%20her%20son.%20They%20both%20say%20it's%20better%20for%20them%20than%20life%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocating-costa-rica-best-thing-california-woman-and-her-son-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wende%20Zomnir%20revolutionized%20makeup%20with%20Urban%20Decay.%20She's%20not%20done%20building%20her%20empire.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wende%20Zomnir.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668c06911aace5b3ada4ff32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWende%20Zomnir.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Wier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20moment%20Wende%20Zomnir%20answers%20my%20call%2C%20it's%20like%20I%20can%20feel%20rays%20of%20California%20sun%20beaming%20through%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20settled%20in%20a%20New%20Jersey%20suburb%2C%20she's%20enjoying%20Newport%20Beach%2C%20California.%20It's%20where%20the%20beauty%20mogul%20runs%20her%20latest%20cosmetics%20venture%20out%20of%20a%20Zomnir-described%20%26quot%3Bsurf%20shack%26quot%3B%20that%20sits%20in%20front%20of%20