20corn%20plastic%2015%20years%20ago.%20And%20Urban%20Decay%20was%20the%20first%20brand%20to%20have%20all%20recycled%20paper%20cartons%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20not%20like%20Caliray's%20wellness%20and%20sustainability%20is%20a%20180%20departure%20from%20Urban%20Decay.%20It%20wasn't%20part%20of%20the%20brand's%20messaging%2C%20but%20it%20was%20always%20part%20of%20my%20personal%20vision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Makeup%20is%20in%20my%20blood'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZomnir%20grew%20up%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20blush%20was%20bold%2C%20and%20hair%20was%20sky-high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20beauty%20memories%20start%20early.%20She%20recalls%20sneaking%20into%20her%20mom's%20bathroom%2C%20the%20smell%20of%20her%20makeup%20drawer%2C%20and%20the%20eyeshadow%20brush%20that%20seemed%20like%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%2C%20fluffiest%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZomnir%20has%20also%20never%20forgotten%20the%20massive%20Calvin%20Klein%20makeup%20kit%20her%20mom%20gifted%20her%20around%20age%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20probably%20the%20best%20Christmas%20gift%20I've%20ever%20gotten%2C%20other%20than%20this%20giant%20diamond%20ring%20my%20husband%20bought%20me%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%20with%20a%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20innate%20love%20for%20makeup%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20college%20job%20selling%20Elizabeth%20Arden%20skincare%20at%20a%20department%20store%20%E2%80%94%20Zomnir%20didn't%20envision%20a%20career%20in%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20customers%20were%20all%20in%20their%2070s%20and%2080s%2C%20and%20the%20women%20I%20worked%20with%20were%20in%20their%2050s%20and%2060s%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20amazing%2C%20like%20moms%20to%20me%2C%20but%20that%20had%20been%20their%20career.%20They'd%20talk%20to%20me%20about%20progressing%20mine%2C%20and%20I%20would%20think%3A%20'Oh%20no%20no%2C%20I'm%20not%20doing%20this.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZomnir%20went%20into%20advertising%2C%20working%20an%20internship%20at%20Leo%20Burnett%20Worldwide%20that%20turned%20into%20a%20job%20working%20on%20cosmetic%20advertising%20accounts.%20Her%20career%20took%20her%20to%20California%20in%20the%20mid-'90s%2C%20where%20her%20life%20changed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZomnir's%20friend%20was%20engaged%20to%20a%20man%20who%20worked%20as%20an%20asset%20manager%20for%20Sandy%20Lerner%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Cisco%20Systems.%20When%20Lerner%20told%20him%20she'd%20set%20her%20sights%20on%20makeup%20and%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20brand%2C%20he%20called%20Zomnir%20and%20asked%20if%20she'd%20like%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20tech%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20thinking%2C%20'How%20can%20we%20possibly%20break%20this%20giant%20beauty%20industry%3F'%20She%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20said%3A%20'Well%2C%20I%20broke%20tech.%20Why%20can't%20we%20break%20beauty%3F'%26quot%3B%20Zomnir%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20jumped%20in.%20Sandy%20and%20I%20started%20Urban%20Decay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBwsvy86Flys%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBwsvy86Flys%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2F