20her%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20ever%20going%20to%20completely%20align%20with%20someone%20else's%20creative%20vision%20for%20your%20brand%3F%20Nope.%20You're%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20brand's%20Moon%20Dust%20eyeshadows%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20love%20the%20new%20package%20they%20put%20them%20in%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20same%20formula%2C%26quot%3B%20Zomnir%20said%20of%20the%20powder%20products%2C%20now%20encased%20in%20see-through%20acrylic%20squares%20rather%20than%20small%2C%20silver%20spheres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20satisfaction%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20of%20the%20things%20I%20created%20are%20still%20the%20top%20sellers%20and%20top%20of%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BMoon%20Dust%20shadows%2C%20the%20Naked%20palettes%2C%20the%2024%2F7%20pencils%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20those%20are%20things%20I%20cooked%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20still%20close%20with%20many%20people%20who%20brought%20the%20brand%20to%20the%20top%20with%20her.%20Zomnir%20said%20she%20attended%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini-reunion%26quot%3B%20with%20ex-Urban%20Decay%20employees%20at%20the%20Caliray%20office%20the%20night%20before%20our%20call.%20Attendees%20included%20L'Or%C3%A9al%20group%20president%20Carol%20Hamilton%2C%20beauty%20veteran%20Tara%20Simon%2C%20and%2C%20in%20true%20Urban%20Decay%20fashion%2C%20lots%20of%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20emotional%20and%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Zomnir%20said%2C%20reflecting%20on%20her%20past%20role.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20was%20there%2C%20I'd%20look%20around%20and%20see%20a%20couple%20hundred%20people%20spread%20across%20a%20few%20buildings%2C%20all%20working%20toward%20a%20really%20unique%20and%20amazing%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wende%20Zomnir.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22