into%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Zomnir%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20use%20glass%20and%20not%20coat%20it%20with%20materials%20that%20render%20it%20unrecyclable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20shiny%2C%20plastic%20lipstick%20tubes%20that%20look%20like%20metal%3F%20They're%20a%20no-go%20for%20Caliray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20beautiful%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0160412021002476%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighly%20toxic%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20really%20pollutes%20the%20air%20environment%20to%20make%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20be%20cognizant%2C%20not%20only%20of%20the%20materials%20we%20use%20but%20how%20we%20treat%20those%20materials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Caliray%20press%20representative%20cites%20the%20brand's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaliraybeauty.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2Fcome-hell-or-high-water-clean-mascara%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECome%20Hell%20or%20High%20Water%20mascara%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20its%20most%20popular%20product.%20It's%20followed%20by%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaliraybeauty.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2Fso-blown%3Fvariant%3D42815579881661%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESo%20Blown%20primer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20brand%20says%20has%20sold%20out%20seven%20times%20at%20Sephora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20products%20are%20also%20extremely%20popular%20on%20TikTok.%20Caliray's%20mascara%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40katie.org%2Fvideo%2F7182695170972863786%3Fis_from_webapp%3D1%26sender_device%3Dpc%26web_id%3D7381479116761663022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20viral%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20still%20regularly%20discussed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fdiscover%2Fmascara-caliray%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%