C%20which%20returned%20for%20a%20record%20third%20term%20after%20winning%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20has%20claimed%20just%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20AAP%20and%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20are%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20that%20fielded%20candidates%20in%20the%20bypolls%20held%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Punjab%2C%20AAP's%20Mohinder%20Bhagat%20won%20the%20Jalandhar%20West%20seat%20by%20over%2023%2C000%20votes.%20In%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20candidates%20have%20taken%20the%20lead%20in%20four%20seats%2C%20with%20BJP%20trailing%20behind%20in%20each%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu's%20wife%20Kamlesh%20Thakur%2C%20who%20made%20her%20electoral%20debut%2C%20won%20the%20Dehra%20elections..%20In%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20leading%20in%20Nalagarh%20too%2C%20while%20BJP's%20Ashish%20Sharma%20is%20ahead%20in%20Hamirpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20TMC%20has%20won%20four%20seats%2C%20with%20its%20candidates%20defeating%20BJP%20opponents%20by%20significant%20margins.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20DMK's%20Anniyur%20Siva%20is%20leading%20by%2058%2C785%20votes%20in%20the%20Vikravandi%20assembly%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Congress%20candidates%20are%20leading%20in%20both%20the%20Badrinath%20and%20Manglaur%20seats%2C%20while%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Kamslesh%20Pratap%20Shahi%20is%20leading%20in%20the%20Amarwar%20seat.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20the%20JD(U)'s%20Kaladhar%20Prasad%20Mandal%20is%20trailing%20behind%20an%20Independent%20candidate%20in%20the%20Rupauli%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%2013%20legislative%20assembly%20seats%20spread%20across%20seven%20states%20began%20on%20Saturday%20morning.%20Voting%20was%20held%20on%20Wednesday%20for%20the%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20bypolls%20were%20the%20first%20since%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20BJP%20winning%20240%20seats%20-%2032%20short%20of%20the%20majority.%20The%20NDA%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20cross%20the%20halfway%20mark%20of%20272%20with%20a%20total%20tally%20of%20293%20seats.%20The%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20clinched%20232%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720865100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F27dfjc1g_bjp-congress-generic_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-leading-in-10-seats-nda-ahead-in-2-aap-wins-jalandhar-west-6095939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20gave%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20has%20come%20out%20on%20top%20in%20the%20by-elections%20to%2013%20Assembly%20seats%20across%20seven%20states.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20won%20eight%20seats%20and%20is%20ahead%20on%20two%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-leading-in-10-seats-nda-ahead-in-2-aap-wins-jalandhar-west-6095939%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-leading-in-10-seats-nda-ahead-in-2-aap-wins-jalandhar-west-6095939%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-leading-in-10-seats-nda-ahead-in-2-aap-wins-jalandhar-west-6095939%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%E2%80%99s%20Sci-Fi%20Adventure%20%E2%80%98Escape%20From%20the%2021st%20Century%E2%80%99%20Picked%20up%20by%20Fortissimo%20Films%22%2C%22content%2