minister%20swims%20in%20Paris%20river%20despite%20unsafe%20levels%20of%20E.coli%20ahead%20of%20Olympics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720862940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-amelie-oudea-castera_6625412.jpg%3F20240713113612%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fparis-2024-olympics-frances-sports-minister-swims-in-river-seine-amid-pollution-concerns-ahead-of-games-13177396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22France's%20sports%20minister%20has%20swum%20in%20the%20River%20Seine%2C%20with%20authorities%20hoping%20the%20move%20will%20show%20it%20is%20clean%20enough%20to%20stage%20swimming%20events%20at%20the%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fparis-2024-olympics-frances-sports-minister-swims-in-river-seine-amid-pollution-concerns-ahead-of-games-13177396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fparis-2024-olympics-frances-sports-minister-swims-in-river-seine-amid-pollution-concerns-ahead-of-games-13177396%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fparis-2024-olympics-frances-sports-minister-swims-in-river-seine-amid-pollution-concerns-ahead-of-games-13177396%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Satellite%20Images%20Indicate%20Huge%20Architectural%20Wealth%20Under%20Bodh%20Gaya%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20geospatial%20analysis%20utilising%20satellite%20images%20and%20ground%20surveys%20has%20found%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20architectural%20wealth%26quot%3B%20buried%20in%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%20and%20its%20surroundings%20in%20Bihar's%20Bodh%20Gaya%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20has%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Heritage%20Development%20Society%20(BHDS)%2C%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20Art%2C%20Culture%20and%20Youth%20Department%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Cardiff%20University%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20four%20holy%20areas%20related%20to%20the%20life%20of%20Lord%20Gautam%20Buddha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBodh%20Gaya%20is%20a%20place%20where%20Lord%20Buddha%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20attained%20enlightenment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20study%20has%20unearthed%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20archaeological%20treasure%20beneath%20the%20soil%20of%20the%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas.%20It's%20a%20huge%20architectural%20wealth%20that%20needs%20further%20excavation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Art%2C%20Culture%20and%20Youth%20Department's%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20Harjot%20Kaur%20Bamhrah%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK-based%20varsity%20and%20the%20BHDS%20are%20cooperating%20in%20the%20project%2C%20'Archaeology%20on%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20Chinese%20traveller%20Xuanzang'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru-based%20National%20Institute%20of%20Advanced%20Studies%20faculty%20member%20MB%20Rajni%2C%20one%20of%20the%20project%20members%2C%20studied%20satellite%20images%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20and%20its%20surroundings%20and%20tried%20to%20correlate%20the%20findings%20with%20the%20description%20of%20'Xuanzang'%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%20at%20Bodh%20Gaya%20comprises%20the%2050-metre-high%20grand%20temple%2C%20the%20Vajrasana%2C%20the%20sacred%20Bodhi%20tree%20and%20other%20six%20sacred%20sites%20of%20Buddha's%20enlightenment%2C%20surrounded%20by%20numerous%20ancient%20stupas%2C%20well%20maintained%20and%20protected%20by%20inner%2C%20middle%20and%20outer%20circular%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BHDS%20in%20association%20with%20Cardiff%20University%20has%20been%20working%20on%20the%20multidisciplinary%20project%20on%20the%20archaeological%20trail%20of%20the%20travel%20of%207th-century%20Chinese%20translator%20monk%2C%20Xuanzang%2C%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20satellite%20images%20from%20the%20last%20several%20years%20show%20an%20alignment%20of%20structures%20to%20the%20north%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20buried%20underground%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bamhrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20images%20show%20the%20shift%20of%20the%20river%20Niranjana%20from%20east%20to%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20remember%20that%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20is%20west%20of%20the%20river%2C%20and%20the%20Sujata%20Stupa%20and%20several%20other%20archaeological%20remains%20are%20located%20east%20of%20the%20river.%20The%20monuments%20and%20other%20archaeological%20remains%20in%20the%20east%20of%20the%20river%20are%20now%20regarded%20to%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20latest%20finding%20shows%20that%20both%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20Sujata%20stupa%20along%20with%20other%20archaeological%20remains%20stood%20on%20the%20same%20river%20bank%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBamhrah%20said%20this%20is%20really%20%26quot%3Bvery%20significant%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20that%20the%20monuments%20and%20other%20archaeological%20remains%2C%20now%20east%20of%20the%20river%2C%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BHDS%20plans%20to%20start%20%26quot%3Bresearch%20to%20delimit%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20complex%20in%20the%20light%20of%20these%20findings%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFresh%20ground-penetrating%20radar%20(GPR)%20survey%2C%20followed%20by%20excavations%2C%20will%20be%20undertaken%20to%20unravel%20the%20buried%20archaeological%20features%20shown%20by%20satellite%20images%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20findings%2C%20BHDS%20Executive%20Director%20Bijoy%20Kumar%20Choudhary%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20fresh%20study%20has%20revealed%20several%20findings%20that%20include%20to%20the%20north%20of%20the%20temple%20premises%2C%20a%20square%20monastery%20complex%20enclosed%20by%20a%20wall%20with%20a%20surrounding%20moat%20and%20an%20extended%20settlement%20to%20its%20north%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiuen%20Tsang%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Xuanzang%2C%20was%20a%20Chinese%20Buddhist%2C%20monk%20scholar%2C%20traveller%20and%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20travelled%20from%20China%20to%20India%20to%20obtain%20Buddhist%20scriptures%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20King%20Harsha%20Vardhan.%20He%20is%20best%20known%20for%20his%20journey%20to%20India%20from%20629%20to%20645%20CE%20and%20his%20efforts%20to%20bring%20over%20657%20Indian%20texts%20into%20China.%20His%20writings%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20development%20of%20Buddhism%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXuanzang's%20travelogue%20of%20India%20helped%20Alexander%20Cunningham%20in%201860s%20and%201870s%20to%20identify%20famous%20sites%20such%20as%20Nalanda%20and%20Vaishali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20square%20wall%20of%20the%20monastery%20complex%20is%20of%20special%20interest%20as%20it%20had%20been%20excavated%20by%20Cunningham%20in%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20but%20no%20further%20excavations%20have%20been%20conducted.%20However%2C%20this%20area%20has%20great%20potential%20for%20systematic%20excavation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpon%20analysing%20satellite%20imagery%2C%20we%20identified%20two%20concentric%20squares%E2%80%A6an%20outer%20square%20enclosing%204.9%20acres%20and%20an%20inner%20one%20enclosing%202.5%20acres.%20Between%20the%20outer%20and%20inner%20squares%2C%20there%20is%20a%20gap%20of%20about%2015%20metres%20and%20in%20the%20south%20and%2020%20meters%20in%20the%20east%20and%20the%20west.%20The%20southern%20boundary%20of%20the%20outer%20square%20is%20approximately%20300%20feet%20from%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20report%20of%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20traces%20of%20the%20monastery%20are%20no%20longer%20visible%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20satellite%20imagery%20revealed%20that%20the%20squares%20overlap%20significantly%20with%20Samanvay%20Ashram%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajni%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20well%20that%20Cunningham%20observed%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20the%20monastery's%20pillared%20court%20might%20be%20one%20of%20the%20two%20wells%20located%20within%20the%20Ashram%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20statue%20of%20Dwarkoji%20Sunderani%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ashram's%20southern%20boundary%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20compound%20wall%20on%20a%20raised%20ridge%2C%20aligns%20with%20the%20southern%20boundary%20of%20the%20outer%20square%2C%20thus%20suggesting%20the%20buried%20remnants%20of%20an%20earlier%20wall%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajni%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720862880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdbsgvelc_mahabodhi-temple-bodh-gaya-ani_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsatellite-images-indicate-huge-architectural-wealth-under-bodh-gayas-mahabodhi-temple-report-6096670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20geospatial%20analysis%20utilising%20satellite%20images%20and%20ground%20surveys%20has%20found%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20architectural%20wealth%26quot%3B%20buried%20in%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%20and%20its%20surroundings%20in%20Bihar's%20Bodh%20Gaya%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%2