Sunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sandeep%20Patil%2C%20Dilip%20Vengsarkar%2C%20Madan%20Lal%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Kirti%20Azad%20are%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20generate%20funds%20for%20Gaikwad's%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20said%20he%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20BCCI%20will%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20to%20the%20former%20India%20head%20coach%20Gaekwad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20sad%20and%20very%20depressing.%20I%20am%20in%20pain%20because%20I%20have%20played%20alongside%20Anshu%20and%20can't%20bear%20to%20see%20him%20in%20this%20state.%20No%20one%20should%20suffer.%20I%20know%20the%20Board%20will%20take%20care%20of%20him.%20We%20are%20not%20compelling%20anyone.%20Any%20help%20for%20Anshu%20will%20have%20to%20come%20from%20your%20heart.%20He%20took%20blows%20on%20his%20face%20and%20chest%20when%20standing%20up%20to%20some%20of%20the%20ferocious%20fast%20bowlers.%20Now%20is%20the%20time%20for%20us%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20him.%20I%20am%20sure%20our%20cricket%20fans%20will%20not%20fail%20him.%20They%20should%20pray%20for%20his%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapil%20Dev%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Fkapil-dev-interview-bcci-financial-help-aunshuman-gaekwad-blood-cancer-illness-news%2Farticle68396130.ece%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legendary%20all-rounder%2C%20however%2C%20rued%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20system%20where%20former%20players%20are%20assisted%20in%20cases%20like%20Anshuman's.%20Kapil%20also%20insisted%20that%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20give%20up%20his%20pension%20if%20the%20situation%20doesn't%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20system.%20It%20is%20great%20to%20see%20this%20generation%20of%20players%20make%20good%20money.%20It%20is%20good%20to%20see%20the%20support%20staff%20members%20also%20being%20paid%20well.%20In%20our%20time%2C%20the%20Board%20did%20not%20have%20the%20money.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20and%20should%20take%20care%20of%20the%20senior%20players%20from%20the%20past.%20But%20where%20do%20they%20send%20their%20contributions%3F%20If%20a%20Trust%20is%20formed%2C%20they%20can%20put%20their%20money%20there.%20But%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20system.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20Trust.%20I%20think%20BCCI%20can%20do%20that.%20They%20do%20look%20after%20the%20players%2C%20former%20and%20present.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20contribute%20by%20donating%20our%20pension%20amount%20if%20the%20family%20allows%20us%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaekwad's%20cricketing%20legacy%20is%20notable.%20He%20played%2040%20Tests%20and%2015%20ODIs%20for%20India%20between%201975%20and%201987%2C%20and%20later%20served%20as%20India's%20head%20coach%20in%20two%20separate%20stints.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720853100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2F9c8iv99s_kapil-dev_640x480_30_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fin-pain-kapil-dev-writes-to-bcci-ready-to-donate-pension-for-ailing-anshuman-gaekwad-6096083%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anshuman%20Gaekwad%2C%20who%20played%2040%20Tests%20and%2015%20ODIs%20for%20India%20between%201975%20and%201987%2C%20and%20later%20served%20as%20India's%20head%20coach%20in%20two%20separate%20stints%2C%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20blood%20cancer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A245%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fin-pain-kapil-dev-writes-to-bcci-ready-to-donate-pension-for-ailing-anshuman-gaekwad-6096083%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fin-pain-kapil-dev-writes-to-bcci-ready-to-donate-pension-for-aili