r%20ending%20his%20career%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20wicket-taking%20charts%20for%20pace%20bowlers%2C%20scalping%20a%20whopping%20704%20wickets.%20But%2C%20after%20helping%20England%20secure%20a%20victory%20in%20his%20farewell%20game%2C%20Anderson%20admitted%20that%20there%20was%20one%20moment%20in%20the%20final%20that%20left%20him%20quite%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post-match%20interview%20with%20Sky%20Cricket%2C%20Anderson%20held%20a%20candid%20chat%20with%20Egland%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nasser%20Hussain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F234-nasser-hussain-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENasser%20Hussain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20under%20who%20he%20made%20his%20debut%20two%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20this%20morning%20was%20quite%20emotional%20with%20the%20two%20teams%20lined%20up%20and%20the%20reaction%20from%20the%20crowd%20was%20pretty%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20yeah%2C%20I'm%20still%20trying%20to%20hold%20them%20%5Btears%5D%20back%20now%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I'm%20just%20really%20proud%20of%20playing%20for%2020-odd%20years.%20%5BIt%5D%20is%20an%20incredible%20effort%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20fast%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20happy%20that%20I've%20made%20it%20this%20far.%20Happy%20that%20I've%20been%20lucky%20enough%20to%20stay%20injury-free%20pretty%20much%20throughout%20my%20career.%20And%20yeah%2C%20play%20for%20England.%20It's%20the%20best%20job%20in%20the%20world%2C%20so%20I've%20been%20privileged%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnderson%20was%20given%20a%20fine%20welcome%20by%20the%20palyers%20in%20both%20teams%20as%20he%20walked%20into%20the%20Lord's%20Cricket%20Ground%20for%20the%20last%20time%20as%20an%20England%20international.%20It%20was%20truly%20an%20emotional%20moment%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20has%20been%20different%20emotions%2C%20been%20so%20up%20and%20down.%20Saw%20my%20girls%20ring%20a%20bell%20on%20day%20one.%20Walking%20out%20today%20with%20both%20teams%20lined%20up%20again%20was%20pretty%20emotional.%20I%20forgot%20what%20I%20was%20actually%20trying%20to%20do%20with%20the%20ball%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said%20at%20a%20press%20interaction%20after%20the%20game.%20%26quot%3BBut%20yeah%2C%20it's%20been%20incredible.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20the%20reaction%20of%20crowds%20was%20phenomenal.%20I%20can't%20get%20my%20head%20around%20it%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20yeah%2C%20it's%20just%20been%20an%20amazing%2020%20years.%20Every%20moment%2C%20every%20great%20sports%20person%2C%20there%20is%20the%20family%2C%20mother%2C%20father%2C%20wife%2C%20kids%2C%20who%20allow%20you%20to%20do%20what%20you've%20done%20for%20so%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Gutted'%20To%20Not%20Get%20The%20705th%20Wicket%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnderson%20could've%20finished%20his%20career%20with%20705%20wickets%20instead%20of%20704%20had%20he%20not%20dropped%20a%20sitter%20to%20give%20West%20Indies'%20Gudakesh%20Motie%20a%20lifeline.%20He%20still%20remains%20disappointed%20about%20that%20spilled%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20gutted%20to%20have%20dropped%20that%20catch%20to%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20yeah%2C%20it's%20been%20an%20amazing%20week.%20I've%20been%20quite%20overwhelmed%20with%20the%20reaction%20of%20the%20crowd%20and%20everyone%20around%20the%20ground%20and%20the%20lads%20as%20well%2C%20just%20proud%20of%20what%20I've%20achieved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20lucky%20to%20play%20with%20some%20amazing%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20most%20talented%20cricketers%20that%20have%20ever%20played%20the%20game%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20some%20really%20good%20blokes%20and%20some%20friends%20that%20I've%20made%20for%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn