0Murmu%20has%20given%20her%20approval%20to%20the%20amendments%20in%20the%20rule%20exercising%20the%20powers%20conferred%20by%20section%2055%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20(34%20of%202019)%20read%20with%20the%20Proclamation%20dated%2031st%20October%202019%20issued%20under%20section%2073%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20MHA%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20made%20the%20rules%20further%20to%20amend%20the%20Transaction%20of%20Business%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Rules%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20rules%20may%20be%20called%20the%20Transaction%20of%20Business%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Union%20Temtory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(Second%20Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendments%20shall%20come%20into%20force%20on%20July%2012%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20publication%20in%20the%20Official%20Gazette%20-%20a%20move%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20speculated%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Transaction%20of%20Business%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Rules%2C%202019%20(hereinafter%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20principal%20rules)%2C%20some%20rules%20have%20been%20inserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20inserted%20sub-rule%20(2A)%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20proposal%20which%20requires%20previous%20concurrence%20of%20the%20Finance%20Department%20with%20regard%20to%20'Police'%2C%20'Public%20Order'%2C%20'All%20India%20Service'%20and%20'Anti%20Corruption%20Bureau'%20to%20exercise%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20under%20the%20Act%20shall%20be%20concurred%20or%20rejected%20unless%20it%20has%20been%20placed%20before%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20principal%20rules%2C%20after%20rule%2042%2C%20rule%2042A%20has%20been%20inserted%20pointing%2C%20%26quot%3BDepartment%20of%20Law%2C%20Justice%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20shall%20submit%20the%20proposal%20for%20appointment%20of%20Advocate-General%20and%20other%20Law%20Officers%20to%20assist%20the%20Advocate-General%20in%20the%20court%20proceedings%2C%20for%20approval%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20inserted%20rule%2042B%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20proposal%20regarding%20grant%20or%20refusal%20of%20prosecution%20sanction%20or%20filing%20of%20an%20appeal%20shall%20be%20placed%20before%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Law%2C%20Justice%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20principal%20rules%2C%20in%20rule%2043%2C%20after%20the%20third%20proviso%2C%20the%20notification%20states%20that%20some%20provisos%20shall%20be%20inserted%2C%20focusing%20on%20matters%20connected%20with%20Prisons%2C%20Directorate%20of%20Prosecution%20and%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%2C%20under%20which%20%26quot%3Bthe%20matters%20shall%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20by%20Administrative%20Secretary%2C%20Home%20Department%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProvided%20also%20that%20in%20respect%20of%20matters%20connected%20with%20posting%20and%20transfer%20of%20Administrative%20Secretaries%20and%20cadre%20posts%20of%20All%20India%20Services%20officers%2C%20the%20proposal%20shall%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20by%20the%20Administrative%20Secretary%2C%20General%20Administration%20Department%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20principal%20rules%20were%20published%20in%20the%20Gazette%20of%20India%20dated%20August%2027%2C%202020%2C%20and%20subsequ