0at%20Credit%20Agricole%20in%20London%2C%20earning%20over%20%24256%2C000%20(about%20Rs%202%20crore)%20annually.%20Despite%20this%20lucrative%20role%2C%20Ms%20Shah%20felt%20unfulfilled%20and%20sought%20a%20more%20meaningful%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20her%20ninth%20year%20in%20banking%2C%20Ms%20Shah%20realised%20her%20job%20was%20neither%20%26quot%3Bchallenging%26quot%3B%20nor%20%26quot%3Bintellectually%20stimulating%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20help%20other%20people%20whilst%20getting%20paid%20for%20it%20and%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20in%20banking%20was%20helping%20corporations%2C%20sovereign%20governments%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20Ms%20Shah%20left%20her%20high-paying%20job%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20content%20creator%20on%20YouTube%2C%20focusing%20on%20personal%20finance.%20Her%20gamble%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20between%20May%202023%20and%20May%202024%2C%20Ms%20Shah%20made%20over%20Rs%208%20crore%20through%20YouTube%20monetisation%2C%20selling%20courses%20and%20products%2C%20doing%20corporate%20talks%20and%20partnering%20with%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20making%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20I%20was%20in%20banking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20not%20chasing%20money%20anymore%20and%20just%20chasing%20what%20I'm%20good%20at%2C%20my%20passion%2C%20and%20what%20I%20really%20enjoy%2C%20it's%20managed%20to%20surpass%20everything%20that%20I%20had%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nischa%20Shah%20started%20her%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20she%20built%20an%20emergency%20fund%20to%20support%20herself%20for%20at%20least%20nine%20months%20after%20quitting%20her%20job.%20Having%20this%20fund%20gave%20her%20the%20confidence%20to%20take%20the%20leap%20and%20pursue%20her%20passion%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shah%20acknowledged%20that%20waiting%20until%20she%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20from%20YouTube%20would%20have%20taken%20longer%20to%20make%20the%20jump.%20Instead%2C%20she%20went%20all-in%2C%20using%20her%20emergency%20fund%20as%20a%20safety%20net.%20She%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bonce-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20my%20life%20in%20my%20own%20hands%20and%20just%20go%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shah's%20success%20on%20YouTube%20was%20not%20instantaneous.%20It%20took%2011%20months%20to%20reach%201%2C000%20subscribers%2C%20but%20a%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20September%202022%20when%20a%20video%20about%20her%20life%20as%20an%20investment%20banker%20went%20viral%2C%20quickly%20gaining%20her%2050%2C000%20subscribers%20and%20earning%20her%20over%20Rs%203%20lakhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENischa%20Shah's%20videos%20cover%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20topics%2C%20from%20%26quot%3BMoney%20Habits%20Keeping%20You%20Poor%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Invest%20Your%20First%20%241000%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3B7%20Passive%20Income%20Ideas%26quot%3B.%20Her%20videos%20receive%20anywhere%20between%201%2C00%2C000%20to%209%20million%20views%20and%20she%20has%20become%20a%20trusted%20figure%20in%20the%20personal%20finance%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720847520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Febn7rgj8_nischa-shah_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnischa-shah-ex-investment-banker-turns-youtuber-earns-rs-8-crore-a-year-6095474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Nischa%20Shah%20traded%20her%20six-figure%20salary%20for%20the%20camera%2C%20becoming%20a%20full-time%20YouTube%20content%20creator.%20Her%20gamble%20paid%20off%2C%20leading%20to%204x%20the%20success%20and%20a%20newfound%20sense%20of%20fulfilment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnischa-shah-ex-investment-banker-turns-youtub