sala%20Lab%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20travel%2C%20she%20would%20jot%20down%20simple%20recipes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20basic%20%3Cem%3Esabzis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eraitas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20curries.%20Despite%20our%20earnest%20efforts%20to%20replicate%20them%20exactly%20as%20written%2C%20my%20father%20and%20I%20could%20never%20quite%20match%20the%20taste%20of%20%3Cem%3Eamma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20humble%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20it%20seems%20straightforward%20but%20proves%20deceptively%20tricky%20to%20perfect.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20this%20tangy%2C%20comforting%20dish%20requires%20minimal%20ingredients%3A%20tamarind%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20crucially%2C%20the%20right%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20(which%20can%20make%20or%20break%20the%20dish!)%2C%20all%20seasoned%20with%20spices%20and%20a%20generous%20dollop%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20then%20why%20does%20my%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20measure%20up%20to%20those%20made%20by%20the%20stalwarts%20of%20the%20household%3F%20Some%20might%20attribute%20it%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emaa%20ka%20pyaar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(mother%E2%80%99s%20love)%2C%20and%20while%20that%20sentiment%20holds%20true%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20scientific%20aspect%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrish%20Ashok%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20unravel%20this%20science%20and%20share%20it%20with%20the%20world.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20work%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20potato%20fry%20far%20outshone%20his%20own.%20How%20does%20one%20achieve%20that%20elusive%20perfect%20crispness%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20add%20some%20spices%20after%20others%20and%20roast%20them%20for%20lesser%20times%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20because%20the%20recipe%20book%20says%20so.%20It%E2%80%99s%20due