Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%3B%20one%20of%2050%20innovators%20at%20the%20National%20Children%20Innovation%20Challenge%20in%20partnership%20with%20UNICEF%20(2023)%2C%20a%20panellist%20at%20the%20World%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20(2023)%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20one%20that%20surpassed%20all%20of%20these%2C%20Nikhil%20says%2C%20was%20the%20recognition%20from%20UNICEF%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20of%20the%20top%20three%20moments%20of%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn%E2%80%99t%20every%20odd%20day%20that%20you%20get%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20legend%20Beckham%20and%20relay%20your%20dreams%20to%20him.%20But%20Nikhil%20did.%20And%20he%20classifies%20this%20as%20his%20top-tier%20moment%3B%20one%20he%20does%20not%20take%20lightly.%20Retracing%20his%20steps%20leading%20up%20to%20it%2C%20he%20says%20it%20was%20fated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20planned%20it.%20I%20never%20applied%20to%20UNICEF.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20applied%20to%20another%20competition%20hosted%20by%20the%20incubation%20centre%20of%20Gujarat%20University%2C%20who%20sent%20my%20project%20to%20UNICEF!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20can%20imagine%20Nikhil%E2%80%99s%20astonishment%20when%20he%20got%20a%20call%20one%20day%20in%20October%202023%20from%20Sanyam%20Chhajed%2C%20programs%20manager%20at%20GUSEC%20(Gujarat%20University%20Startup%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Council)%2C%20informing%20him%20about%20an%20exhibition%20where%20a%20few%20dignitaries%20would%20be%20present.%20One%20thing%20led%20to%20another%20and%20on%2013%20November%2C%202023%2C%20Nikhil%20was%20one%20of%20five%20chosen%20students%20from%20across%20India%20presenting%20his%20work%20to%20Beckham%2C%20UNICEF%20Goodwill%20Ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2